title: Week 1 NFL Recap, Rams Big Day, Jags Look Like A Sleeper (Football 09/11)
description:
Will Brinson and Nick Kostos break down all the action from Week 1 of the NFL season, and wonder if the Giants are a trainwreck, if the Rams could win the NFC West, whether the Seahawks offensive line is their Achilles Heel, if the 49ers are trash, whether the Jaguars are a sleeper in the AFC South, if Falcons fans should be worried about their win over the Bears and how good the Panthers really can be.
